data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the excellent Sandy location, east of State St.! This well-constructed brick rambler offers the perfect blend of convenience and charm. With easy access to the interstate, you'll find yourself just moments away from all amenities, restaurants, Real Stadium, Southtowne Expo, shopping, parks, and more  truly, the best of Sandy is at your fingertips! Step inside this inviting residence and discover an updated kitchen that will inspire your inner chef. The brand new carpet adds a touch of luxury, and beneath it lies the hidden treasure of original hardwood on the main floor, waiting to be revealed and refinished for an added touch of class. This home boasts an enormous attached 2-car garage, providing both convenience and ample storage space. The quiet neighborhood and nearby schools make it an ideal setting for families or anyone seeking a peaceful retreat. With move-in readiness and a thoughtful combination of modern updates and classic features, this home is sure to please even the most discerning buyer. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Sandy gem your own  schedule a showing today and envision yourself living in the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience!  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from an appraisal .  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
